    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/e0a09f7bba39dab15bd2f990f6527e05.avif?t=1685988819\" width=598 height=310 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/d4920e0adb592f534b9c516f94ea8064.webp?t=1685988819\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras_big/d4920e0adb592f534b9c516f94ea8064.webp?t=1685988819 width=800 height=43 /></span><br>巨大地震引起了大陆中央火山的爆发，达沃斯大陆笼罩在灾难的乌云之下。道路被封锁，森林被烧毁，天空被火山灰覆盖。大陆上的所有生物都苦不堪言，维持已久的种族平衡最终因此被打破。主宰大陆的三大种族，人类、精灵、兽族正卷入无法避免的冲突漩涡之中<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/b30e8a1b27d4a0dc838a50f5a1f2a6c4.webp?t=1685988819\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras_big/b30e8a1b27d4a0dc838a50f5a1f2a6c4.webp?t=1685988819 width=800 height=43 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/998c91d837cb801dcaa5a9fb37e54279.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=348 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>请选择你的种族</li></ul></strong>三大种族各具特色，在人类、精灵、兽族中选择自己喜欢的种族开始游戏吧。各族间不同风味的建筑、单位和英雄将给大家带来不一样的乐趣。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/dd8a6348ad1b08468c23566ad9ff244f.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=248 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 开采资源，建设生产设施，升级技术。</li></ul></strong>开采资源，可用于修建建筑物。建造招募军队的集结点，或在研究室中强化军队。再建新基地以获取更多的资源。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/0fda99ee0627cdf6b48cee677528fb8c.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=248 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>消耗资源组建军团</li></ul></strong>试试消耗灰石和黄金来组建强大的军团。 强大的军队能带领战争走向胜利。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/789f36e6da4db6c59226498fd43df911.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=248 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>睿智的战略眼光是制胜秘诀</li></ul></strong>&quot;如何最高效利用有限的资源和时间&quot;，&quot;如何制定直击要害的战略&quot;,胜负将依此见分晓。 试试以完美的战略和高超的玩法打败对方玩家吧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/3ab71f5e779aa71efc15320bc26ae2fb.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=248 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>召唤英雄</strong></li></ul>各英雄单位均拥有强大能力值，并各具独特技能。 最大限度地提高英雄单位的技能，可扭转不利的战场形势，或在有利局面下获得压倒性的胜利。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/3c46843dfeefe9f6160149ab48c04285.webp?t=1685988819\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras_big/3c46843dfeefe9f6160149ab48c04285.webp?t=1685988819 width=800 height=43 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1582500/extras/f31242d42b42a284fe7205651aa9dd8b.avif?t=1685988819\" width=616 height=248 /></span>\t\t\t\t<br>Purple War紫晶之战具备多种游戏模式，可满足不同玩家的需求。 [自定义战役模式]中可自由选择一对一的单人战役，或是8人以内的多人战役，[战役模式]中可在Purple War紫晶之战中经历有趣的故事，[合作战役模式]中和其他玩家携手击退强敌。不同的战役，同一个守望，紫晶之战已准备好为司令浴血奋战。",
